milestones.description: Erasmus and van Lingen's 198-run partnership is NAM's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 151 between Erasmus and Davin
Jonty Jenner and Lawrenson's 80-run partnership is JER's highest for the 4th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 38 between Jonty Jenner and Lawrenson
Blampied and Jonty Jenner's 24-run partnership is JER's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 14 between Benjamin Ward and Lawrenson
Jonty Jenner and Benjamin Ward's 30-run partnership is JER's highest for the 6th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 16 between Benjamin Ward and Sumerauer
Jonty Jenner and Sumerauer's 5-run partnership is JER's highest for the 7th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 1 between Anthony Hawkins-Kay and Sumerauer
Perchard and Sumerauer's 32-run partnership is JER's highest for the 9th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 2 between Perchard and Jake Dunford
Erasmus and van Lingen's 198-run partnership is NAM's highest for any wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 162 between van Lingen and Erasmus
Jonty Jenner's 76 is the highest individual score in ODIs (for JER), surpassing Lawrenson's 66
Carlyon has broken the record for playing the most ODIs (2) for JER, going past Jake Dunford
